This Repository update the Ansible inventory from AWS dynamically.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
•	Copy the following files into the controller node to enable dynamic inventory.
https://github.com/mevasaroj/AWS/blob/main/ec2.ini
https://github.com/mevasaroj/AWS/blob/main/ec2.py

•	Change the permission of both file to executable
$ chmod +x ec2.py
$ chmod +x ec2.ini

•	Pass AWS_ACCESS_KEY and AWS_SECRET_KEY in the ec2.ini file for authentication

•	Run the ec2.py to update the Ansible inventory automatically.
$ ./ec2.py - - list

•	Validate the Ansible inventory file by running following command.
$ ansible all — —list-hosts
